If anyone is still having trouble with SSH access to the repo, make sure you have your key listed in <https://gitlab.cecs.anu.edu.au/profile/keys>

If you have more than one key, make sure you're using the correct one with your git client, look at `ssh-add` command

if it still doesn't work the last step would be to manually add your key to the deploy key list here: <https://gitlab.cecs.anu.edu.au/u5568225/GuidestarLaser/settings/repository>
